snippet.title: Terrible Teeth Promo
snippet.description: Terrible Teeth is an up and coming action arcade mobile game from Vile Media LLC. Play as Cornelius, a heroic kernel of corn trying to save his friends from certain doom in the mouth of a mutated monster!
